Map by: Larnon
Thanks to: Masotek, Shogun
----------------------------------------------
A deathrun map in a volcano.It has some new traps. There are 61 cts and 3 ts.Lava goes up to the first floor when someone reaches to second floor but you got like 20 secs to reach second floor.Also if someone reaches to finnish the lava goes up again and cts have 10 secs to reach to finnish again.Its still beta so report any bugs or glitches.
---------------------------------------------
b5:Fixed some traps speed and bugs, add  new buttons , added a secret.now ts have more time to get to roof.

Edit:Fixed glitch on circle_trap.

Steam id:larnon

final:improved/fixed/changed some traps, re-textured.
